        <p>Effective communication between social organizations and donors is vital for building strong relationships and ensuring project success.</p>
        <div class="feature-box">
            <h2>Functionalities</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Interactive communication channels</li>
                <li>Personalized messaging based on donor preferences</li>
                <li>Real-time status updates on projects</li>
                <li>Automated notification systems for project updates</li>
                <li>Monitoring and tracking of communication engagement levels</li>
